{
  "chapter": 28,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十八回\"要人命的金钱\"。弄堂内四名黄衫人押送四十九名江湖豪客，独腿首领到场审问。黄衫老人宣布规矩：头顶铜钱不可掉落，否则必死。水蛇胡媚因打喷嚏掉落铜钱，被处死前请求让情人杨承祖动手。杨承祖虽百般不愿，但自己头顶铜钱也掉落，被迫一刀杀死胡媚后自尽。随后独腿人与青面汉子对峙，揭露一封神秘信件引百余名江湖人聚集此地欲自相残杀的阴谋。独腿人自称前来化解祸事，青面汉子不为所动。二人最终以兵器谱排名对峙——铁拐第八对蛇鞭第七，剑拔弩张。本章展现了黄衫势力的恐怖规矩和江湖人的冷酷无情。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_si_ge_huang_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "四个黄衫人",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_si_ge_huang_shan_ren",
      "text": "全都带来了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫人",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_ren",
      "text": "一共有多少位？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫人",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "四十九人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_ren",
      "text": "你能确定他们全是为那件事来的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "在下等已调查确实，这些人都是在这三天内赶来的，想必都是为了那件事而来，否则怎会不约而同地来到这里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "调查清楚了就好，咱们可不能错怪了好人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "咱们的意思，这些人明白了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "只怕还未明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "那么你就去向他们说明白吧。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们是什么人，各位想必已知道了，各位的来意，我们也清楚得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位想必都接到了这同样的一封信，才赶到这里来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但凭各位的这点本事，就想来这里打主意，只怕还不配，所以各位还是站在这里，等事完再走的好，我们可以保证各位的安全，只要各位站着不动，绝没有人会来伤及各位毫发。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位想必都知道，我们不到万不得已时，是不伤人的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "我们的规矩，你不知道？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "知……知道。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "既然知道，你就未免太不小心了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "晚辈绝不是故意，求前辈饶我这一次。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "我也知道你不会是故意的，却也不能坏了规矩，规矩一坏，威信无存，你也是老江湖了，这道理你总该明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "大哥，你……你也不替我说句话？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_fei",
      "speaker_name": "胡非",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "我说了话又有什么用？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_hu_fei",
      "text": "我明白……我不怪你！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "text": "小杨你呢？我……我就要走了，你也没有话要对我说？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "text": "你难道连看都不愿看我一眼？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们大家看看，这就是我的情人，这人昨天晚上还对我说，只要我对他好，他不惜为我死的，但现在呢？现在他连看都不敢看我，好像只要看了我一眼，就会得麻疯病似的……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么叫做情？什么叫做爱？一个人活着又有什么意思？真不如死了反倒好些，也免得烦",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "这又何苦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "你本来可以死得舒服些的，又何苦多此一举。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "但你临死之前，我们还可以答应你一个要求。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "这……这也是你们的规矩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "我无论要求什么事，你们都答应我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "你若有什么未了的心愿，我们可以替你去做，你若有仇未报，我们也可以替你去复仇！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "能死在我们手上的人，运气并不错。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "text": "我既已非死不可，不知可不可以选个人来杀我？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "那也未尝不可，却不知你想选的是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "text": "就是他，杨承祖！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "speaker_name": "杨承祖",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "你……你这是什么意思？你难道想害我？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "text": "你对我虽是虚情假意，我对你却是情真意浓，只要能死在你的手上，我死也甘心了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫老人",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "杀人只不过是举手之劳而已，你难道从未杀过人么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huang_shan_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "黄衫大汉",
      "listener": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "text": "这把刀快得很，杀人一定用不着第二刀！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "speaker_name": "杨承祖",
      "listener": "char_huang_shan_da_han",
      "text": "我不……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "胡媚",
      "listener": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "text": "你说过，我若死了，你也活不下去，现在你果然要陪我死了，你这人总算还有几分良心……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_cheng_zu",
      "speaker_name": "杨承祖",
      "listener": "char_hu_mei",
      "text": "你这妖妇，你好毒的心肠！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "阁下是什么人，我们已知道了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "我们是什么人，阁下想必也已知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "近两年来不知道你们的人，只怕很少。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "阁下不远千里而来，想必也是为了这封信来的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "阁下可知道这封信是谁写的么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "据我们所知，江湖中接到这样信的至少也有一百多位，但却没有一个人知道信是谁写的，我们也曾四下打听，却连一点线索也没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "若连你们也打听不出，还有谁能打听得出！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "我们虽不知道信是谁写的，但他的用意我们却已明白。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "他将江湖中成名的豪杰全引到这里来，为的就是要大家争夺埋藏在这里的宝物，然后自相残杀！他才好得渔翁之利。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "既然如此，你们为何要来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "正因他居心险恶，所以我们才非来不可！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "我们到这里来，就为的是要劝各位莫要上那人的当，只要各位肯放手，这一场祸事就可消弭于无形了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "你们的心肠倒真不错。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "我们只希望能将大事化小事，小事化无事，让大家都能安安静静地过几年太平日子。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "其实此间是否真有宝藏，大家谁也不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "正是如此，所以大家若是为了这种事而拼命，岂非太不值得了？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "但我既已来了，好歹也得看他个水落石出，岂是别人三言两语就能将我打发走的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "如此说来，阁下是不肯放手的了？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "我就算放了手，只怕也轮不到你们！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "除了阁下外，我倒想不出还有谁能跟我们一争长短的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "果然好功夫，难怪百晓生作兵器谱，要将你这只铁拐排名第八。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独腿人",
      "listener": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "text": "阁下的蛇鞭排名第七，我早就想见识见识了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_mian_han_zi",
      "speaker_name": "青面汉子",
      "listener": "char_dui_tui_ren",
      "text": "我也正想要你们见识见识！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 28,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    }
